    <title>lnv:DOC-HEADING <lnpid>id-RU02-32057</lnpid>
    </title>

    <body>
        <p>
            <b>Scenario1:</b></p>
           <p> If <sourcexml>lnv:DOC-HEADING</sourcexml> starts with "COPYRIGHT" as a text the its
            mapping will be <targetxml>doc:metadata/pubinfo:pubinfo/copyright</targetxml>.</p>
                

        <example>
            <title>Source XML</title>
            <codeblock>

&lt;lnv:DOC-HEADING&gt;COPYRIGHT © 2013 KLINE PRESTON PUBLISHING, INC. AND KLINE PRESTON LAW GROUP,
P.C. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED&lt;/lnv:DOC-HEADING&gt;


	</codeblock>
        </example>

        <example>
            <title>Target XML </title>
            <codeblock>

&lt;doc:metadata&gt;
    &lt;pubinfo:pubinfo&gt;
        &lt;copyright&gt;COPYRIGHT © 2013 KLINE PRESTON PUBLISHING, INC. AND KLINE PRESTON LAW GROUP,
        P.C. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED&lt;/copyright&gt;
    &lt;/pubinfo:pubinfo&gt;
&lt;/doc:metadata&gt;

	</codeblock>
        </example>
        <p><b>Scenario2:</b></p>
        <p>                   If <sourcexml>lnv:DOC-HEADING</sourcexml> contains running text as a
            heading, then its mapping will be <targetxml>dc:metadata/dc:title</targetxml>.</p>
        
        <example>
            <title>Source XML</title>
            <codeblock>

&lt;lnv:DOC-HEADING&gt;THE LEGISLATION ON COPYRIGHT OF THE RUSSIAN FEDERATION&lt;/lnv:DOC-HEADING&gt;


	</codeblock>
        </example>
        
        <example>
            <title>Target XML </title>
            <codeblock>

&lt;dc:metadata&gt;
   &lt;dc:title&gt;THE LEGISLATION ON COPYRIGHT OF THE RUSSIAN FEDERATION&lt;/dc:title&gt;
&lt;/dc:metadata&gt;

	</codeblock>
        </example>
        
